    PPC 208: demux 1004, mux 1002.  Started around 5:45.  Running at least
       for an hour.

    PPC 227: demux 1100, mux 1100.  Started around 5:05.  Died in 35 min.
    Reason: due to special treatment in CleanCut.
    Solution: DO NOT generate picStat for the first TP after a channel is
              turned on, but instead wait for the first picture boundary.
              This means there will be some TPs in the beginning of the
              TP queue which has no corresponding PicStat.  They will be
              cleaned up in the sendVideo() function in output Task.
  
