Plan for multiple-channel DPI:
  - Use PidBuf for all inter-task communication instead of using
    PicHandle and SpliceCmd structures.
  - Define clear inter-task message structures.
    => New header file common/dspmsg.h
  - Modify Switcher Task to handle both picHandle and spliceReqCmd
    with the same input queue.  This means we can use the switcher task
    to handle splice request, hence saving one task.


